title: BBC R4 Documentary - 'The Lair Of Vincent Price' sp7
description:
BBC R4 Documentary - 'The Lair Of Vincent Price'
Broadcast in the 'Kaleidoscope Feature' series
Presented by Nigel Andrews
Produced by John Boundy
Broadcast February 17, 1989
Coded from tape at 128/44.1
Some sibilance, but readily audible throughout

BBC Kaleidoscope interview with Vincent Price
in which he talks about his career.
